  "subject": "Upgrade to SO common 1.19.0 (Java 17)",
  "commit_message": "Upgrade to SO common 1.19.0 (Java 17)\n\n- Update parent POM to org.onap.so:so:1.19.0\n- Set Java 17 as compilation target\n- Update so-core-version to 1.19.0\n- Upgrade H2 to 2.1.214 and Flyway to 8.5.13\n- Update Docker base image to eclipse-temurin:17-jre-alpine\n- Remove CryptoUtils usage (removed in SO 1.19.0)\n- Remove unused shazamcrest and openpojo dependencies\n- Add .mvn/jvm.config for swagger-codegen Java 17 compat\n- Fix Flyway migration SQL for H2 2.x (int(11) -> int)\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4364\nChange-Id: I73b49e1d2541eae10c7c809bdc3ef4975b2f5a50\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
